Valor Bot is a suite of open source software for WhatsApp Application based on Baileys WebSocket API.

_Some highlight features:_
• Downloader (youtube, fb, insta, etc.)
• Sticker Creator
• Tag All
• Games
• Internet Search (google text & image search)
• AFK
• Broadcast

*Valor Bot Source*
https://bit.ly/Valor_Bot

*Valor Bot Test Group*
https://bit.ly/Valor_Bot_Test

*Valor Bot Bug Report*

*Valor Bot Feature Request*
